Cut 171 tokens (-687 bytes) from a.c and lib/note.c while preserving all functionality.

Changes:
- GA macro: deduplicated buffer grow+append pattern in cmd_cat mode 3
- is5d(): replaced 3 verbose 5-digit priority checks with strspn helper
- task_todir(): folded stat/isdir guard into function, simplified 4 callsites
- task_add_p(): merged duplicate task-add code paths into shared helper

Test commands:
  sh a.c                          # build (should succeed silently)
  A_BENCH=1 ./adata/local/a help  # basic dispatch
  A_BENCH=1 ./adata/local/a task l | head -5  # task listing (uses is5d, task_add_p)
  A_BENCH=1 ./adata/local/a hi    # trivial cmd
  ./adata/local/a diff main       # verify negative tokens
  cat adata/local/.chk 2>/dev/null || echo OK  # no checker errors
